{"word":"G2302 - θέατρον - théatron - theh'-at-ron - Spectacle","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θέατρον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>théatron"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>theh'-at-ron"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Spectacle"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"அரங்கசாலை, வேடிக்கை - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a theatre"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G2300 - θεάομαι - theáomai - theh-ah'-om-ahee/2300\">G2300</a>; <i>a place for public show</i> (&ldquo;theatre&rdquo;), that is, general <i>audience room</i>; by implication a <i>show</i> itself (figuratively): - spectacle, theatre."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2301 - θεατρίζω - theatrízō - theh-at-rid'-zo/2301\">G2301</a>, <a href=\"#/G2302 - θέατρον - théatron - theh'-at-ron/2302\">G2302</a>"}]}